<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>The Trading Suite | Aurivon Capital Co-Working</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        :root {
            --gold: #c5a059;
            --dark-surface: #12161b;
            --bg-black: #0a0e12;
            --text-light: #f4f4f4;
            --accent-blue: #00d2ff; /* Represents the fiber/tech glow */
        }

        body {
            background-color: var(--bg-black);
            color: var(--text-light);
            font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }

        /* Hero Section */
        .hero {
            padding: 100px 5% 60px;
            text-align: center;
            background: linear-gradient(rgba(10,14,18,0.8), rgba(10,14,18,0.8)), 
                        url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1554469384-e58fac16e23a?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=1920'); /* Office placeholder */
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            border-bottom: 2px solid var(--gold);
        }

        .hero h2 {
            color: var(--gold);
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 4px;
            font-size: 1rem;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .hero h1 {
            font-size: 3.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        /* Business Stats/Features */
        .stats-bar {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 40px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            padding: 40px 5%;
            background: var(--dark-surface);
        }

        .stat-item {
            text-align: center;
        }

        .stat-item i {
            color: var(--gold);
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        /* Main Content */
        .content-section {
            max-width: 1100px;
            margin: 60px auto;
            padding: 0 5%;
        }

        .grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 30px;
        }

        .card {
            background: var(--dark-surface);
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            border-left: 3px solid var(--gold);
            transition: 0.3s;
        }

        .card:hover {
            background: #1a2027;
        }

        .card h3 {
            color: var(--gold);
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        /* Pricing/Access Section */
        .pricing {
            background: #0f1318;
            padding: 80px 5%;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .price-box {
            border: 1px solid rgba(197, 160, 89, 0.3);
            max-width: 400px;
            margin: 40px auto;
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }

        .price-tag {
            font-size: 3rem;
            color: var(--gold);
            font-weight: bold;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        .cta-btn {
            background: var(--gold);
            color: black;
            padding: 18px 40px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 800;
            display: inline-block;
            border-radius: 4px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .hero h1 { font-size: 2.2rem; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <section class="hero">
        <h2>Aurivon Business Hub</h2>
        <h1>The Trading Suite</h1>
        <p>Ultra-Low Latency Co-Working for Professional FX & Gold Traders</p>
    </section>

    <div class="stats-bar">
        <div class="stat-item">
            <i class="fas fa-bolt"></i>
            <strong>1ms Latency</strong>
            <p>Direct Fiber Access</p>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-item">
            <i class="fas fa-shield-alt"></i>
            <strong>Secure Access</strong>
            <p>24/7 Biometric Entry</p>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-item">
            <i class="fas fa-microchip"></i>
            <strong>Workstations</strong>
            <p>Dual-Monitor Ready</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <section class="content-section">
        <div class="grid">
            <div class="card">
                <h3>Institutional Infrastructure</h3>
                <p>We’ve eliminated the bottleneck. Our Singapore facility is engineered with a dedicated fiber backbone specifically for trade execution, reducing slippage and ensuring your orders hit the market first.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <h3>Veteran Alpha</h3>
                <p>Don't trade in isolation. Join a community of veteran FX and Gold specialists. Share strategies, discuss market sentiment, and sharpen your edge in a professional environment.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <h3>Proprietary Funding</h3>
                <p>Consistent traders aren't just renters—they're potential partners. Residents get direct access to Aurivon Capital’s performance-based hiring and capital funding pipelines.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="pricing">
        <h2>Secure Your Desk</h2>
        <div class="price-box">
            <h3>Trader Day Pass</h3>
            <div class="price-tag">$35<span>/day</span></div>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 25px; color: #b0b3b8;">High-speed fiber, ergonomic desk, and unlimited premium coffee.</p>
            <a href="#" class="cta-btn">Join the Waitlist</a>
        </div>
    </section>

</body>
</html>
